Remove Spaces from String | Remove all spaces from a given string. |

import java.util.*;
class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        String str = "Hello world ";
       
        System.out.println("remove spaces in string: "+ removeSpace(str));
        
    }
    public static String removeSpace(String str){
        return str.replaceAll("\\s+","");
    }
    
}

output:
remove spaces in string: Helloworld


" " targets just the space character.

"\\s+" targets all whitespace (space, tab, newline, etc.) one or more times.
